tldr: The user requested a comprehensive review and implementation of missing
  features for a sleep questionnaire application. The agent successfully
  implemented a tiredness severity scale, COMISA detection, insufficient sleep
  syndrome detection, outbound resource links, weighted EDS scoring, expanded
